C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprizes%20political%20power%20over%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20wind-up%20of%20a%20major%20property%20developer%20like%20Evergrande%20could%20complicate%20the%20Chinese%20government's%20efforts%20to%20support%20the%20property%20sector%20and%20ensure%20the%20timely%20delivery%20of%20pre-sold%20homes%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Fern%20Wang%2C%20a%20senior%20researcher%20at%20KT%20Capital%20Group%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20in%20a%20note%20published%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartkarma.com%2Finsights%2Fevergrande-s-wind-up-ruling-implications%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESmartkarma%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20the%20PRC%20court%20may%20potentially%20reject%20the%20judgment%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20potential%20harm%20to%20public%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20People's%20Republic%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20mainland%20China%20runs%20on%20a%20different%20legal%20system%20from%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20so%20whether%20Chinese%20authorities%20will%20comply%20with%20the%20order%20also%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20Offshore%20creditors%20are%20owed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F01%2F29%2Fbusiness%2Fevergrande-ordered-to-liquidate-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2425%20billion%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20court%20document%20showed%2C%20per%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHao%20Hong%2C%20the%20partner%20and%20chief%20economist%20at%20Grow%20Investment%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20said%20it's%20unlikely%20for%20shareholders%20of%20Hong%20Kong-listed%20China%20Evergrande%20Group%20to%20get%20anything%20out%20of%20the%20company's%20wind-up%20process%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fchina-evergrande-ordered-liquidate-by-hong-kong-court-2024-01-29%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3