ong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20has%20released%20new%20draft%20guidelines%20for%20recruitment%20for%20faculty%20positions%20in%20universities%2C%20sparking%20widespread%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20these%20guidelines%2C%20if%20no%20qualified%20candidates%20are%20identified%20for%20reserved%20seats%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20categories%2C%20those%20seats%20will%20be%20filled%20by%20candidates%20from%20the%20unreserved%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20a%20protest%20took%20place%20today%20in%20front%20of%20the%20UGC%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi%2C%20denouncing%20the%20draft%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudent%20organisations%20from%20various%20colleges%20and%20universities%20in%20Delhi%20participated%20in%20this%20protest%2C%20with%20the%20Students%E2%80%99%20Federation%20of%20India%20(SFI)%2C%20Krantikari%20Yuva%20Sangathan%20(KYS)%2C%20All%20India%20Students%E2%80%99%20Association%20(AISA)%2C%20and%20Democratic%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%20(DSU)%20prominent%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20demonstration%2C%20students%20expressed%20their%20dissent%20against%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20UGC%2C%20raising%20slogans%20and%20displaying%20posters%20outlining%20their%20various%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20the%20opposition%20to%20the%20decision%2C%20the%20UGC%20on%20January%2028%20clarified%20that%20the%20reserved%20posts%20in%20higher%20education%20institutions%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20de-reserved%20and%20will%20not%20be%20de-reserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30142704%2FMG_7774.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22reservation