et%20for%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%E2%80%99s%20public%20meeting%20in%20Patna%20this%20afternoon%2C%20K.C.%20Tyagi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpatna%2Fkc-tyagi-returns-as-jdus-chief-spokesperson-just-2-months-after-omission-of-his-name-from-partys-office-bearers-list%2Farticleshow%2F100425998.cms%5C%22%3Erecently%20reinstated%3C%2Fa%3E%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20leader%2C%20has%20stirred%20a%20hornet%E2%80%99s%20nest%20by%20reportedly%20calling%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eachhoot%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20untouchable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fjdus-kc-tyagi-takes-achhoot-congress-dig-over-mallikarjun-kharges-nitish-kumar-exit-pre-planned-jab-101706515950770.html%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20was%20reacting%20to%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20remark%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20exit%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpre-planned%E2%80%9D.%20But%20JD(U)%20leader%20Tyagi%20on%20Monday%20calling%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%98achhoot%E2%80%99%20(untouchable)%20has%20significance%20as%20the%20phrase%20has%20stopped%20being%20used%20for%20deep%2C%20casteist%20resonance%2C%20especially%20given%20that%20Kharge%20himself%20belongs%20to%20a%20Dalit%20community%20from%20Karnataka.%20Untouchability%20has%20been%20abolished%20by%20Article%2017%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20and%20the%20use%20of%20the%20phrase%20itself%20is%20considered%20demeaning%20and%20derogatory%2C%20if%20not%20a%20criminal%20offence%20in%20some%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETyagi%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20said%20that%20had%20the%20exit%20been%20pre-planned%2C%20JD(U)%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20brought%20regional%20allies%20to%20join%20INDIA.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20we%20bring%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yad