20Hawa%20Mahal%20constituency%20in%20December%20last%20year%20by%20a%20narrow%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20he%20had%20been%20seen%20inspecting%20meat%20shops%20and%20urging%20the%20administration%20to%20take%20action%20against%20what%20he%20called%20were%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20slaughterhouses%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Che%20won%E2%80%99t%20let%20Jaipur%2C%20which%20is%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Choti%20Kashi%E2%80%99%2C%20become%20Karachi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Frajasthan-fir-against-hawa-mahal-mla-balmukunt-acharya-for-alleged-assault-on-sc-community-member%5C%22%3ERajasthan%3A%20FIR%20Against%20Hawa%20Mahal%20MLA%20Balmukund%20Acharya%20for%20Alleged%20Assault%20on%20SC%20Community%20Member%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuslims%20being%20targeted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20does%20he%20have%20to%20do%20to%20what%20we%20wear%3F%20We%20are%20coming%20here%20to%20study%20and%20we%20will%20study.%20We%20will%20not%20stop%20our%20protest%20till%20the%20Baba%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20apologise.%20He%20always%20targets%20Muslims%2C%20sometimes%20over%20meat%2C%20shops%20run%20by%20Muslims%2C%20now%20over%20hijab.%20Today%20he%20wants%20to%20end%20hijab%20in%20school%2C%20tomorrow%20he%20may%20stop%20us%20from%20wearing%20hijab%20in%20school.%20Muslim%20students%20at%20the%20school%20are%20being%20targeted.%20Wearing%20hijab%20is%20our%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20protesting%20students%20told%20reporters%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcharya%20is%20facing%20allegations%20of%20assaulting%20and%20spitting%20on%20a%20person%20belonging%20to%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20community%20in%20Peethawas%20village%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Mohammad%20Aslam%20Khan%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Alpsankhak%20Vikash%20Sanstha%20said%20that%20most%20of%20the%20girl%20students%20in%20the%20school%