20any%20complaint%20they%20will%20be%20investigating%20it.%20No%20FIR%20has%20been%20lodged%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20said%20the%20commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MLA%20from%20Adarsh%20Nagar%20Rafeek%20Khan%20reached%20the%20protest%20site%20on%20Monday%20and%20slammed%20Acharya%20for%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20listened%20to%20the%20protesting%20women.%20The%20type%20of%20environment%20Balmukund%20wants%20to%20create%20here%20is%20a%20direct%20attack%20to%20the%20Ganga-Jamuni%20%3Cem%3Etehzeeb%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Jaipur.%20The%20Baba%20should%20immediately%20apologise.%20We%20will%20not%20stay%20quiet%20on%20this%20and%20he%20will%20have%20to%20apologise%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khan%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkarnataka-hijab-ban-students-approach-sc-for-interim-relief-to-write-exams%5C%22%3EHindutva%20groups%20had%20backed%20a%20government%20ban%20on%20hijab%20in%20Karnataka%20schools%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706604335000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30135817%2FUntitled-design-7-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Facharya-balmukund-rajasthan-hijab-protests%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hawa%20Mahal%20MLA%20and%20Hindu%20priest%20%E2%80%98Baba%E2%80%99%20Balmukund%20Acharya%20said%20the%20environment%20of%20a%20school%20had%20been%20spoiled%20because%20some%20students%20wore%20the%20hijab.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Facharya-balmukund-rajasthan-hijab-protests%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zee-Sony%20merger%3A%20NCLT%20issues%20notice%20to%20Sony%20to%20file%20reply%20in%20three%20weeks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706604331000%2C%22visual%22%3A