hings.%20I%20think%20women%20face%20this%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20and%20I'm%20barely%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20faced%20so%20much%20judgement%20including%20hatred%20over%20the%20years%20for%20things%20that%20don't%20even%20matter.%20I%20think%20women%20should%20start%20getting%20equal%20respect%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706599740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ftigqkrn_divya-chess_625x300_30_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Findian-chess-player-divya-deshmukh-alleges-sexism-by-spectators-in-tournament-4958786%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teenager%20said%20while%20male%20players%20were%20getting%20their%20share%20of%20spotlight%20purely%20for%20their%20game%2C%20the%20women%20were%20judged%20for%20aspects%20which%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20their%20ability%20on%20the%20chess%20board.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SEVENTEEN%20fans%20in%20Korea%20launch%20boycott%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706599441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107254246%2Cimgsize-258250.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fseventeen-fans-in-korea-launch-boycott-amidst-controversy-over-encore-concert-series%2Farticleshow%2F107254297.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107254297.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20focal%20point%20of%20the%20criticism%20revolves%20around%20the%20group's%20decision%20