0scrutiny%20following%20a%20damning%20account%20by%20a%20passenger%20who%20alleged%20a%20distressing%20experience%20during%20a%20recent%20flight%20from%20Ahmedabad%20to%20Bengaluru%20with%20his%20pet%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%2C%20the%20passenger%20%C2%A0Lakshay%20Pathak%20outlined%20significant%20issues%20that%20marred%20his%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CHorrible%20experience%20with%20Pet%20Travel%20in%20Akasa%20Air%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20and%20I%20were%20travelling%20with%20our%20pet%20Shih%20Tzu%20on%2026th%20Jan%20Flight%20from%20Ahmedabad%20to%20Bangalore.%20The%20flight%20that%20was%20intended%20to%20leave%20at%2010%3A20%20pm%20left%20at%201%3A40%20AM.%20It%20being%20our%20first%20time%20with%20pet%20travel%20we%20reached%20the%20airport%203%20hrs%20in%20advance.%20So%20a%20delay%20of%20more%20than%203%20hrs%20and%20we%20have%20already%20spent%20over%206%20hrs%20in%20the%20airport%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20passenger%20highlighted%20the%20unhelpful%20attitude%20of%20the%20ground%20staff%20and%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%2C%20specifically%20noting%20their%20incompetence%20in%20handling%20pet-related%20queries.%C2%A0%E2%80%9COn%20call%20%26amp%3B%20mail%20a%20very%20different%20picture%20was%20painted%20at%20buying%20a%20pet%20ticket%20for%20Rs5000%20would%20enable%20comfortable%20travel%20of%20the%20pet%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20and%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20huge%20delay%20the%20airport%20staff%20was%20adamant%20on%20not%20letting%20the%20pet%20ever%20out%20of%20the%20container.%20While%20sitting%2C%20thrice%20the%20airport%20security%20came%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20not%20even%20let%20him%20lie%20on%20the%20floor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20revealed%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20provision%20for%20pets%20to%20relieve%20themselves.%20All%20the%20washrooms%20in%20the%20airport%20have%20blowers%20that%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20noise%2C%20leaving%20no%20chance%20for%20pets%20to%20pee.%20Additionally%2C%20neither%20the%20ground%20staff%20nor%20the%20CISF%20assisted%20in%20terms%20of%20going%20out%20of%20the%20airport%20and%20coming%20back%20inside.%20The%20ground%20staff%20told%20me%20that%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20relieve%20my%20pet%20in%20the%20flight's%20washroom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pathak%20expressed%20frustration%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20'special%20seat'%20to%20accommodate%20pet%20travel%2C%20not%20even%20in%20the%20last%20row.%20For%20the%20first%2045%20minutes%20of%20the%20flight%2C%20my%20dog%20kept%20crying.%20To%20console%20him%2C%20I%20placed%20his%20container%20on%20my%20lap%2C%20allowing%20his%20head%20to%20breathe%20for%20a%20while.%20Apparently%2C%20this%20was%20also%20'not%20allowed.'%20The%20pet%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20near%20your%20leg%20space%20below%20the%20seat%2C%20and%20we%20all%20know%20how%20limited%20that%20space%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20flight%20crew%20as%20%26quot%3Buntrained%20and%20unprofessional%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pathak%20claimed%20that%20attempts%20to%20console%20his%20distressed%20pet%20by%20allowing%20it%20to%20breathe%20outside%20the%20container%20were%20met%20with%20resistance%20from%20a%20steward.%20The%20crew's%20lack%20of%20understanding%20regarding%20pet%20comfort%20during%20the%20flight%20further%20added%20to%20the%20passenger's%20frustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20is%20the%20treatment%20given%20to%20dogs%20in%20the%20cabin%2C%20I%20cannot%20imagine%20what%20treatment%20is%20given%20to%20those%20travelling%20in%20the%20cargo%2C%26quot%3B%20Pathak%20stated.%20He%20questioned%20the%20value%20of%20the%20pet%20ticket%2C%20given%20the%20reported%20restrictions%20and%20lack%20of%20accommodation%20for%20the%20animal.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20Pet%20Ticket%20for%3F%20The%20torture%20that%20was%20provided%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%