t%20Directorate%20officials%20look%20to%20question%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%20While%20official%20sources%20claim%20that%20Mr%20Soren%20is%20%26quot%3Bmissing%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20past%2024%20hours%2C%20his%20party%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20has%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20safe%20and%20in%20touch%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ED%20sources%2C%20they%20have%20no%20information%20about%20Mr%20Soren's%20whereabouts.%20The%20chartered%20plane%20on%20which%20he%20travelled%20from%20Ranchi%20to%20Delhi%20is%20parked%20at%20Delhi%20airport.%20The%20phones%20of%20several%20people%20part%20of%20his%20staff%20are%20switched%20off.%20His%20BMW%20car%20in%20Delhi%20has%20been%20seized%20by%20the%20ED.%20His%20driver%20has%20also%20been%20questioned%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%20Some%20documents%20and%20cash%20worth%20Rs%2036%20lakh%20have%20been%20made%2C%20said%20sources.%20ED%20officials%20yesterday%20visited%20his%20homes%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20Jharkhand%20Bhavan%2C%20but%20could%20not%20find%20him.%20Mr%20Soren%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20left%20his%20Delhi%20residence%20late%20on%20Sunday%20night.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20ED%20has%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20his%20office%2C%20informing%20that%20he%20will%20be%20available%20for%20questioning%20at%201%20pm%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20Jharkhand%20unit%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20%26quot%3Babsconding%26quot%3B%20and%20urged%20Governor%20CP%20Radhakrishnan%20to%20take%20note.%20The%20Governor%20has%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bkeeping%20a%20watch%20on%20the%20overall%20situation%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20job%20of%20the%20Governor%2C%20I%20am%20doing%20it.%20We%20will%20cross%20the%20bridge%20when%20it%20comes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20BJP%20president%20Babulal%20Marandi%20has%20alleged%20that%20according%20to%20s