a%20kimono%20and%20displayed%20at%20an%20airport.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAuditors%20said%20the%20doll%20was%C2%A0%26quot%3Bextremely%20expensive%26quot%3B%20and%C2%A0%26quot%3Bgrossly%20inappropriate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAuditors%20have%20rapped%20the%20Tokushima%20Prefectural%20Government%20for%20purchasing%20an%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20expensive%26quot%3B%20sex%20doll%20to%20promote%20the%20city's%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20tourism%20policy%20division%20said%20it%20paid%20424%2C440%20Japanese%20yen%2C%20or%20%242%2C880%2C%20for%20the%20doll%2C%20which%20was%20used%20in%20a%20tourist%20exhibition%20at%20the%20Tokushima%20Awaodori%20Airport%20in%202017%2C%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmainichi.jp%2Fenglish%2Farticles%2F20240129%2Fp2a%2F00m%2F0na%2F010000c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMainichi%20Shimbun%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exhibition%20was%20meant%20to%20promote%20the%20prefecture's%20traditional%20indigo-dyeing%20art%2C%20so%20the%20doll%20was%20clad%20in%20an%20indigo-dyed%20summer%20kimono%2C%20per%20the%20Mainichi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20initially%20used%20a%20pair%20of%20cheaper%20mannequins%20%E2%80%94%20not%20the%20sex%20doll%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20exhibition%20in%20June%202017.%20Rental%20for%20both%20mannequins%20cost%20around%20%24180%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Mainichi%20Shimbun's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20July%2C%20an%20unnamed%20male%20official%20decided%20to%20replace%20the%20mannequins%20with%20the%20sex%20doll.%20He%20then%20went%20about%20procuring%20the%20sex%20doll%2C%20which%20he'd%20concluded%20would%20be%20a%20crowd-pleaser%2C%20according%20to%20an%20audit%20report%20of%20the%20case%20obtained%20by%20the%20Mainichi%20Shimbun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20auditors%20dismissed%20the%20prefecture's%20claims%20that%20the%20sex%20doll%20was%20more%20effective%20at%20drawing%20tourists%20than%20the%20mannequins.%20The%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20expen