ress%20Club%20of%20India%20on%20Monday%20(January%2029).%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20tried%20tirelessly%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20but%20our%20efforts%20have%20not%20received%20a%20response.%20Media%20is%20now%20our%20community%E2%80%99s%20only%20hope%20to%20raise%20our%20voice%20to%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20representative%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20days%2C%20numerous%20news%20reports%20have%20emerged%2C%20with%20the%20Kuki%20community%20alleging%20that%20Assam%20Rifles%20is%20causing%20issues%20for%20their%20volunteers.%20Since%20the%20violence%20began%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Meiteis%20expressed%20satisfaction%20with%20Manipur%20Police%2C%20while%20the%20Kukis%20were%20happier%20with%20the%20central%20forces.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20the%20Kukis%20have%20accused%20Assam%20Rifles%20of%20attacking%20their%20people.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20reporter%20asked%20about%20this%20during%20the%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20still%20content%20with%20the%20Assam%20Rifle%2C%20but%20there%20are%20two%20officers%20who%20are%20causing%20problems%20for%20us.%20These%20officers%20exhibit%20bias%20against%20our%20community.%20One%20is%20Rahul%20Jain%2C%20stationed%20at%20Moreh%2C%20and%20the%20other%20is%20Akash%20Oinam%2C%20a%20Meitei%20officer%20posted%20in%20the%20Saikul%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20violence%2C%20we%20brought%20this%20issue%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20Central%20government%20and%20demanded%20the%20placement%20of%20unbiased%20officers%20in%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20W.L.%20Hangshing%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Kuki%20People%E2%80%99s%20Alliance.%20Another%20representative%2C%20Mary%20Grace%2C%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20officers%20are%20assisting%20Meitei%20militant%20groups%20in%20infiltrating%20our%20buffer%20zone%20and%20aiding%20them%20in%20harming%20our%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community%20also%20called%20for%20the%20immediate%20and%20complete%20withdrawal%20of%20Meitei%20State%20Security%20Forces%20from%20Moreh.%20Several%20months%20ago%2C%20during%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Manipur%2C%20he%20issued%20assurances%20to%20the%20community%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eastmojo.com%2Fmanipur%2F2023%2F05%2F31%2Fmanipur-amit-shah-agrees-to-recall-police-commandos-in-moreh-more%2F%5C%22%3E%20regarding%20this%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20yet%20to%20take%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20demand%20they%20raised%20is%20to%20enforce%20a%20buffer%20zone%20and%20requested%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20empower%20Central%20forces%20to%20prevent%20Meitei%20militants%20from%20intruding%20on%20and%20attacking%20Kuki-Zo%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20they%20urged%20the%20Central%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Crein%20in%E2%80%9D%20the%20Manipur%20government%20immediately.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Manipur%20Government%20is%20now%20under%20the%20control%20of%20Meitei%20militant%20groups%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20also%20called%20for%20assistance%20in%20securing%20admissions%20for%20Kuki-Zo%20students%20in%20educational%20institutes%20outside%20the%20state%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20complete%20their%20studies.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20hundreds%20of%20Kuki-Zo%20students%20who%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20continue%20their%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706590948000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30102922%2FIMG_9246.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ffew-commanding-officers-of-assam-rifles-creating-issues-kuki-zo-groups%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Delhi%2C%20representatives%20from%20Manipur%20said%20th