ti%2C%20along%20with%20two%20Canadian%20nationals%20identified%20as%20Hells%20Angels%20members%2C%20Damion%20Patrick%20John%20Ryan%20and%20Adam%20Richard%20Pearson%2C%20conspired%20in%20a%20murder-for-hire%20scheme%20to%20kill%20two%20people%20in%20Maryland%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20defected%20from%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20are%20said%20to%20have%20conspired%20between%20December%202020%20through%20March%202021%2C%20with%20Zindashti%20using%20encrypted%20messaging%20to%20recruit%20agents%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20US%20and%20carry%20out%20the%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20alleged%2C%20Mr.%20Zindashti%20and%20his%20team%20of%20gunmen%2C%20including%20a%20Minnesota%20resident%2C%20used%20an%20encrypted%20messaging%20service%20to%20orchestrate%20an%20assassination%20plot%20against%20two%20individuals%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20US%20Attorney%20Andrew%20Luger%20for%20the%20District%20of%20Minnesota.%20%26quot%3BThanks%20to%20the%20skilled%20work%20of%20federal%20prosecutors%20and%20law%20enforcement%20agents%2C%20this%20murder-for-hire%20conspiracy%20was%20disrupted%20and%20the%20defendants%20will%20face%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ's%20indictment%20alleges%20that%20Zindashti%20hired%20the%20Hells%20Angels%20bikers%20to%20conduct%20the%20assassination%20in%20January%202021.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fopa%2Fpr%2Fone-iranian-and-two-canadian-nationals-indicted-murder-hire-scheme%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edepartment's%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pearson%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3Bshooting%20is%20probably%20easiest%20thing%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bon%20it.%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20recommended%20%26quot%3B2%20guys%20go%20with%20proper%20equipment.%26quot%3B%20Pearson%20said%20he%20would%20encourage%20the%20recruits%20for%20the%20job%20to%20%26quot%3Bshoot%20%5Bthe%20victim%5D%20in%20the%20head%20a%20lot%20%5Bto%5D%20make%20example%26