nting%20annual%20leave%20with%20pay%20to%20workers%2C%20not%20forming%20a%20welfare%20fund%20for%20employees%20and%20not%20distributing%205%25%20of%20its%20dividends%20to%20its%20staff%2C%20the%20reports%20by%20%3Cem%3EProthom%20Alo%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20AP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%20and%20the%20three%20other%20employees%20have%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20my%20lawyers%20have%20convincingly%20argued%20in%20court%2C%20this%20verdict%20against%20me%20is%20contrary%20to%20all%20legal%20precedent%20and%20logic%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-67858016%5C%22%3Ethe%20BBC%20quoted%20Yunus%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20statement%20after%20the%20January%201%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20call%20for%20the%20Bangladeshi%20people%20to%20speak%20in%20one%20voice%20against%20injustice%20and%20in%20favour%20of%20democracy%20and%20human%20rights%20for%20each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20our%20citizens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20Al%20Mamun%2C%20Yunus%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EProthom%20Alo%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20court%20on%20Sunday%20fixed%20the%20next%20date%20for%20hearing%20in%20the%20case%20to%20March%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEighty-three-year-old%20Yunus%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20in%202006%2C%20is%20credited%20with%20lifting%20millions%20out%20of%20poverty%20through%20his%20microfinancing%20bank%2C%20the%20Grameen%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20AP%2C%20Yunus%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20say%20he%20is%20being%20targeted%20due%20to%20his%20poor%20relations%20with%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98authoritarian%E2%80%99%20leader%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20reports%20that%20while%20the%20reason%20for%20their%20apparent%20feud%20is%20unclear%2C%20his%20supporters%20have%20said%20Hasina%E2%80%99s%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20discredit%20him%20because%20he%20had%20