76%2Fassam-woman-builds-community-centre-for-education-empowering-tribal-communities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelm%20of%20the%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Shivprabha%20is%20bringing%20about.%20Thrust%20into%20the%20working%20world%20at%20a%20young%20age%20after%20he%20lost%20his%20father%20when%20he%20was%20just%20eight%20years%20old%2C%20Sainwar%20says%20he%20learnt%20to%20push%20the%20boundaries%20early%20on%20in%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20sell%20newspapers%20when%20I%20was%20younger%20and%20then%20began%20giving%20tuitions%20and%20working%20at%20a%20tyre%20repair%20company%20when%20I%20was%20older.%20The%20money%20I%20earned%20helped%20me%20continue%20my%20education%20till%20Class%2012.%20But%20then%20I%20hit%20a%20roadblock.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExorbitant%20fees%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318386%2Fdelhi-police-constable-than-singh-runs-free-school-for-slum-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprofessional%20courses%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20Sainwar%20reconsider%20his%20options.%20The%20few%20thousands%20he%20had%20managed%20to%20save%20up%20through%20the%20years%20were%20no%20match%20for%20the%20engineering%20fees.%20But%20help%20comes%20to%20those%20who%20persist%2C%20he%20shares.%20His%20professors%20stepped%20in%20and%20funded%20his%20engineering%20course%2C%20where%20Sainwar%20shone%20and%20topped%20his%20batch%20in%20the%20final%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20he%20began%20preparing%20in%20earnest%20for%20the%20GATE%20exam%20(an%20entrance%20examination%20for%20postgraduate%20programs%20in%20engineering).%20Recalling%20his%20own%20struggles%20that%20he%E2%80%99d%20seen%20in%20his%20academic%20journey%2C%20Sainwar%20decided%20to%20donate%20the%20books%20he%20had%20purchased%20to%20his%20college%20library%20once%20the%20exam%20was%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image