n%20settled%20in%20the%20village.%20They%20already%20had%20sex%2C%20might%20as%20well%20get%20them%20married%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20shows%20the%20stark%20reality%20for%20many%20abused%20women%2C%20which%20is%20scary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%20and%20mindset%2C%20the%20relentless%20pursuit%20of%20justice%20in%20the%20face%20of%20pressure%20and%20intimidation%20to%20drop%20the%20case%20is%20worth%20every%20plaudit.%20Ranjit%2C%20his%20wife%20Jaganti%2C%20and%20Kiran%20remain%20unfazed.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20think%20of%20Kiran%2C%20every%20fear%20goes%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20Ranjit%20in%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRanjit%20simply%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20status%20quo%20and%2C%20because%20of%20that%2C%20showed%20us%20that%20change%20is%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pahuja%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20Kiran%20turned%2018%20by%20the%20time%20the%20editing%20of%20the%20documentary%20film%20was%20completed%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20come%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20not%20wanting%20to%20remain%20hidden.%20She%20wished%20to%20encourage%20other%20survivors%20through%20her%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20film%20would%20also%20connect%20with%20many%20on%20its%20quotient%20of%20resilience%20and%20how%20we%20can%20go%20that%20extra%20mile%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20protecting%20those%20we%20love.%20On%20its%20surface%2C%20it%20may%20feel%20like%20a%20film%20from%20India%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20actually%20a%20film%20about%20what%20it%20feels%20to%20be%20a%20human.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20continues%20to%20resonate%2C%20touching%20something%20deep%20inside%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pahuja%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Federal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20now%20Oscar-nominated%20film%20documentary%20%E2%80%98To%20Kill%20A%20Tiger%E2%80%99%20was%20released%20in%20September%202022%20and%20has%20been%20screened%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https