%20ball%20with%20full%20force%2C%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20even%20move%20her%20little%20finger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20being%20extraordinary%20in%20every%20way%2C%20I%20suddenly%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20feed%20myself%2C%20bathe%20myself.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20get%20out%20of%20bed.%20It%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337346%2Fdisability-inspiring-veena-ambarish-kari-dosa-food-cart-bengaluru-jp-nagar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereally%20broke%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20parents%20stood%20by%20her%20like%20rocks%20through%20this%20entire%20ordeal.%20Her%20father%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20take%20care%20of%20her%20and%20they%20moved%20to%20Tiruvannamalai%2C%20a%20spiritual%2C%20temple%20town%2C%20to%20heal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreethi%20then%20tried%20to%20get%20admission%20to%20a%20correspondence%20course%20for%20BSc%20Psychology%2C%20but%20she%20was%20rejected%20as%20there%20were%20practical%20classes%20and%20the%20colleges%20were%20not%20disabled-friendly.%20There%20were%20no%20elevators%20or%20ramps.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20remembers%20being%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20do%20people%20like%20you%20come%20to%20study%3F%E2%80%9D%20Her%20father%2C%20her%20biggest%20cheerleader%2C%20bought%20her%20books%20to%20study%2C%20and%20motivated%20her%20to%20educate%20herself%2C%20degree%2C%20or%20no%20degree.%20He%20would%20read%20out%20to%20her%20from%20various%20books%20across%20genres%2C%20from%20fiction%20to%20educational%20books%20to%20spiritual%20books.%20She%20would%20fight%20with%20him%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20go%20of%20her%20hand%2C%20and%20helped%20her%20overcome%20her%20pain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20she%20started%20piecing%20her%20life%20together%2C%20another%20big%20wave%20hit%20her.%20Her%20father%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20in%202007%2C%20and%20just%20four%20days%20later%2C%20her%20mother%2C%20too%2C%20had%20a%20heart%20attack%20and%20had%20to%20have%20a%20bypass%20surgery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20world%20was%20rocked%20again.%20I%20had%20an%2080-year-old%20grandmother%20to%20take%20care%20of.%20We%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Chennai%20for%20the%20surgery.%20We%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20we%20would%20manage%20the%20next%20meal%20or%20who%20would%20even%20help%20me%20sit%20on%20my%20wheelchair.%20I%20had%20to%20start%20earning%20money%20and%20life%20seemed%20difficult%20all%20over%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Preethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20her%20friends%20reiterated%20the%20need%20for%20her%20to%20get%20a%20formal%20degree.%20She%20took%20up%20BSc%20Medical%20Sociology%20as%20it%20had%20no%20practical%20exams.%20She%20also%20did%20MSc%20in%20Psychology%20despite%20wanting%20to%20do%20counselling%20psychology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20counsel%20people%20as%20my%20voice%20is%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20have.%20I%20was%20denied%20admission%20and%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20psychology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20too%20deserve%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rehabilitation%20is%20provided%20free%20of%20cost%20at%20Soulfree%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338795%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERehabilitation%20is%20provided%20free%20of%20cost%20at%20Soulfree%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20as%20she%20grappled%20with%20getting%20an%20education%20and%20a%20treatment%20for%20her%20mother%2C%20she%20encountered%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337564%2Ffree-tiffin-service-meals-for-senior-citizens-rakesh-panchal-gujarat-donate-now%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20deaths%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20shook%20her%20to%20the%20core.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20wanting%20to%20take%20care%20of%20them%2C%20two%20paraplegic%20girls%20who%20I%20knew%20were%20apparentfly%20poisoned%20by%20their%20families.%20It%20left%20me%20wondering%2C%20India%20has%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20populations%20and%20yet%20there%20is%20no%20place%20for%20a%20quadriplegic%20or%20a%20paraplegic%20person%20to%20live%20with%20dignity.%20There%20was%20no%20one%20to%20take%20care%20of%20me%20when%20my%20mom%20got%20sick%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20started%20researching%20and%20found%20that%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20many%20long-term%20rehabilitation%20centres%20or%20places%20that%20offered%20care%20for%20people%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injuries.%20Her%20mother%20then%20persuaded%20her%20to%20start%20such%20a%20haven%20that%20provides%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%20for%20people%20with%20severe%20disabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20laughed%20off%20the%20idea%20as%20I%20had%20no%20clue%20about%20running%20or%20financing%20a%20non-profit%20organisation.%20But%20the%20death%20of