thikeyan%20(25)%2C%20was%20bedridden%20after%20he%20fell%20from%20a%20tree%20three%20years%20ago.%20He%20came%20to%20Soulfree%20six%20months%20back%20and%20is%20now%20able%20to%20walk%20with%20a%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20bedridden%20made%20me%20contemplate%20ending%20my%20life.%20I%20also%20had%20some%20bedsores.%20I%20was%20using%20a%20wheelchair.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20walk%20using%20a%20stick%20and%20do%20my%20daily%20chores%20and%20have%20learnt%20tailoring%20and%20computers%2C%20which%20I%20will%20use%20to%20support%20myself%20once%20I%E2%80%99m%20back%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Karthikeyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreethi%20is%20also%20working%20with%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20to%20include%20rehabilitation%20in%20the%20government%20insurance%20scheme.%20She%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20advisory%20board%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98Welfare%20of%20the%20Differently-Abled%E2%80%99%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20people%2C%20after%20a%20spinal%20cord%20injury%2C%20go%20home%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20The%20government%20should%20work%20on%20providing%20proper%20recognition%20for%20our%20disability%20and%20with%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20people%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20gave%20her%20the%20strength%20to%20do%20so%20much%20while%20she%20herself%20faced%20innumerable%20challenges%20in%20her%20daily%20life%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-14-1705936051.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Preethi's%20parents%20were%20her%20greatest%20support%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-14-1705936051.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2